
log_file(3)          LPC LIBRARY FUNCTIONS            log_file(3)

NAME
     log_file() - append a message to a log file

SYNOPSIS
     void log_file(string file, string message);

DESCRIPTION
     Append a message to a log file.  The log directory is to  be
     specified in the runtime configuration file.  The log direc-
     tory is automatically prepended to the filename.

SEE ALSO
     write_file(3), write_bytes(3).


